p-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/03/monster-hunter-wilds-how-many-chapters-how-long.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=7.8125%2C0%2C84.375%2C100\u0026amp;w=1920 1920w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/03/monster-hunter-wilds-how-many-chapters-how-long.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=7.8125%2C0%2C84.375%2C100\u0026amp;w=2048 2048w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/03/monster-hunter-wilds-how-many-chapters-how-long.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=7.8125%2C0%2C84.375%2C100\u0026amp;w=2400 2400w\" src=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/03/monster-hunter-wilds-how-many-chapters-how-long.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=7.8125%2C0%2C84.375%2C100\u0026amp;w=2400\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ccite\u003eImage: Capcom\u003c/cite\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv id=\"zephr-anchor\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe \u003cstrong\u003eSane Jewel\u003c/strong\u003e is a \u003ca href=\"https://www.polygon.com/monster-hunter-wilds-guide/533238/decorations-how-to-get-equip-grind\"\u003edecoration\u003c/a\u003e in \u003cem\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.polygon.com/game/monster-hunter-wilds/40940\"\u003eMonster Hunter Wilds\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/em\u003e that is a bit challenging to locate, but the effects granted by it are worth the trouble.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eIf you’re struggling on how to get the Sane Jewel, or what it does, read on. We cover what the Sane Jewel is and tell you how to get one in \u003cem\u003eMonster Hunter Wilds\u003c/em\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp id=\"what-is-the-sane-jewel-in-monster-hunter-wilds\"\u003e\u003ch2\u003eWhat is the Sane Jewel in Monster Hunter Wilds?\u003c/h2\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe Sane Jewel is a decoration type that can \u003cstrong\u003erandomly drop at the end of hunts in \u003cem\u003eMonster Hunter Wilds\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e. But because it’s a rarity-5 decoration, many hunters haven’t found the jewel until they’ve hit a very high hunter rank.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe Sane Jewel provides the skill Antivirus, which could be useful in high-level fights found deeper in the game. Antivirus’ skill description is: “Once infected, makes it easier to overcome the Frenzy and increase Affinity when cured.”\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/03/Monster-Hunter-Wilds_20250314102231.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0,0,100,100\" data-pswp-height=\"2160\" data-pswp-width=\"3840\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"The menus for the Sane Jewel and its Antivirus skill. The Antivirus skill boosts the player’s Affinity 3% after recovering from Frenzy at Level 1, 6% at Level 2, and 15% at Level 3. \" data-chromatic=\"ignore\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" sizes=\"(max-width: 639px) 100vw, (max-width: 1023px) 50vw, 700px\" srcset=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/03/Monster-Hunter-Wilds_20250314102231.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=256 256w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/03/Monster-Hunter-Wilds_20250314102231.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=376 376w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/03/Monster-Hunter-Wilds_20250314102231.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=384 384w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/03/Monster-Hunter-Wilds_20250314102231.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=415 415w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/03/Monster-Hunter-Wilds_20250314102231.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u002